495111419/image2017-4-4%2017%3A34%3A18.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1491320058000&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"495116210\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image2017-4-4 17:34:18.png\" data-base-url=\"https://confluence.int.net.nokia.com\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"495111419\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" /></span>\r\nThe \"Mount\" button has been changed to \"Unmount\" and a new drive has appeared in the File Browser :\r\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" src=\"https://confluence.int.net.nokia.com/download/attachments/495111419/image2017-4-4%2017%3A33%3A43.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1491320024000&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"/download/attachments/495111419/image2017-4-4%2017%3A33%3A43.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1491320024000&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"495116207\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image2017-4-4 17:33:43.png\" data-base-url=\"https://confluence.int.net.nokia.com\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"495111419\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" /></span></li>\r\n 	<li></li>\r\n</ol>','How to install sshfs','','inherit','closed','closed','','181-revision-v1','','','2018-10-19 02:24:36','2018-10-19 02:24:36','',181,'http://45.77.202.181/?p=186',0,'revision','',0),(188,1,'2018-10-30 07:45:14','2018-10-30 07:45:14','一般情况，我们使用状态机，会分成下面几个步骤\r\n1、在协议栈回调中（一般是网络框架的线程，例如TCP/IP协议栈poll到读写事件回调给用户，又例如SIP协议栈收到报文回调给上层），找到对应的状态机对象。\r\n2、读取消息，封装成事件，调用状态机的process_event\r\n3、状态机更具自身状态，判断合适的guard，调用适当的action，进入下一个State\r\n\r\n阅读了CP-UE中的状态机处理\r\n1、在协议栈回调和状态机之间有一层Dispatch用于接触协议栈和状态机的耦合\r\n2、状态机在初始状态init即会自动执行一个action，第一次向Dispatch进行注册\r\n3、事件Event可分为成功、失败，超时，成功即进入预定的下一个状态\r\n4、重点在于Action, 每次进入一个State时，执行的Action可包括向Dispatch注册相应回调，开启定时器判断超时，发送数据，在接收数据回调用进入下一个状态。\r\n\r\n至于好处，感觉似乎更灵活','CP-UE代码中状态机阅读感想','','publish','open','open','','cp-ue%e4%bb%a3%e7%a0%81%e4%b8%ad%e7%8a%b6%e6%80%81%e6%9c%ba%e9%98%85%e8%af%bb%e6%84%9f%e6%83%b3','','','2018-10-30 08:26:46','2018-10-30 08:26:46','',0,'http://45.77.202.181/?p=188',0,'post','',0),(189,1,'2018-10-30 07:45:14','2018-10-30 07:45:14','一般情况，我们使用状态机，会分成下面几个步骤\r\n1、在协议栈回调中（一般是网络框架的线程，例如TCP/IP协议栈poll到读写事件回调给用户，又例如SIP协议栈收到报文回调给上层），找到对应的状态机对象。\r\n2、读取消息，封装成事件，调用状态机的process_event\r\n3、状态机更具自身状态，判断合适的guard，调用适当的action，进入下一个State\r\n\r\n阅读了CP-UE中的状态机处理\r\n1、在协议栈回调和状态机之间有一层Dispatch用于接触协议栈和状态机的耦合\r\n2、状态机在初始状态init即会自动执行一个action，第一次向Dispatch进行注册\r\n3、事件Event可分为成功、失败，超时，成功即进入预定的下一个状态\r\n4、重点在于Action, 每次进入一个State时，执行的Action可包括向Dispatch注册相应回调，开启定时器判断超时，发送数据，在接收数据回调用进入下一个状态。\r\n\r\n至于好处，感觉似乎更灵活','CP-UE代码中状态机阅读感想','','inherit','closed','closed','','188-revision-v1','','','2018-10-30 07:45:14','2018-10-30 07:45:14','',188,'http://45.77.202.181/?p=189',0,'revision','',0),(190,1,'2018-10-30 08:25:05','2018-10-30 08:25:05','首先这些个类或函数的作用是用来替换早起union，因为早些时候的union是非类型安全的\r\n\r\nboost::any 和 boost::variant的区别\r\nboost::any一个类，包含特定的访问函数，但类型不限定\r\nboost::variant是一个模板类，模板形参规定了特定的几个类型，可以boost::get访问\r\nboost::apply_visitor则是用来访问boost::variant，由于boost::variant可能是多种类型，想让其调用对应的重载函数，就要使用boost::apply_visitor实际使用的使用lamda配合auto很方便，如\r\n\r\n<code class=\"EnlighterJSRAW\" data-enlighter-language=\"cpp\">auto successfulCallback = [&amp;](const messages::f1ap::CuConfigurationUpdateOutcome&amp; msg) {</code>\r\n<code class=\"EnlighterJSRAW\" data-enlighter-language=\"cpp\"> boost::apply_visitor([this](const auto&amp; msg) { this-&gt;onMessage(msg); }, msg);</code>\r\n<code class=\"EnlighterJSRAW\" data-enlighter-language=\"cpp\"> };</code>\r\n\r\nc++17增加的相应的支持\r\n如std::any std::variant std::visit\r\n\r\n<strong>以下文章转自：<a href=\"http://www.jb51.net/article/95814.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">http://www.jb51.net/article/95814.htm</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Boost.Variant</strong>\r\n\r\nVariant库包含一个不同于union的泛型类，用于在存储和操作来自于不同类型的对象。这个库的一个特点是支持类型安全的访问，减少了不同数据类型的类型转换代码的共同问题。\r\n\r\n<strong>Variant 库如何改进你的程序？</strong>\r\n\r\n•对用户指定的多种类型的进行类型安全的存储和取回\r\n\r\n•在标准库容器中存储不同类型的方法\r\n\r\n•变量访问的编译期检查\r\n\r\n•高效的、基于栈的变量存储\r\n\r\nVariant 库关注的是对一组限定类型的类型安全存储及取回，即非无类的联合。<code>Boost.Variant </code>库与<code> Boost.Any </code>有许多共同之外，但在功能上也有不同的考虑。在每天的编程中通常都会需要用到非无类的联合(不同的类型)。保持类型安全的一个典型方法是使用抽象基类，但这不总是可以做到的；即使可以做得，堆分配和虚拟函数的代价也可能太高。你也可以尝试用不安全的无类类型，如 void* (它会导致不幸)，或者是类型安全得无限制的可变类型，如 <code>Boost.Any</code>. 这里我们将看到 <code>Boost.Variant</code>，它支持限定的可变类型，即元素来自于一组支持的类型。\r\n\r\n下面将浅谈variant的几种访问方法，一起来学习学习吧。\r\n\r\n<strong>使用boost::get</strong>\r\n<div class=\"jb51code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_899793\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter cpp\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\"><a class=\"toolbar_item command_help help\" href=\"http://www.jb51.net/article/95814.htm#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">?</a></div>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::variant&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">, std::string&gt; v;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">v = </code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"Hello world\"</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">std::cout &lt;&lt; boost::get&lt;std::string&gt;(v) &lt;&lt; std::endl;</code></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n使用<code>boost::get</code>来访问，需要给出原始类型，并且这样做不安全，若类型错误，程序将会抛出异常。\r\n\r\n<strong>使用RTTI</strong>\r\n<div class=\"jb51code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_766693\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter cpp\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\"><a class=\"toolbar_item command_help help\" href=\"http://www.jb51.net/article/95814.htm#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">?</a></div>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\">10</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\">11</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\">12</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\">13</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\">14</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\">15</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\">16</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\">17</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number18 index17 alt1\">18</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number19 index18 alt2\">19</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">void</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">var_print(boost::variant&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">, std::string&gt;&amp; v)</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">if</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">(v.type() == </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">typeid</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">(</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">))</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">    </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">std::cout &lt;&lt; get&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">&gt;(v) &lt;&lt; std::endl;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">else</code> <code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">if</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">(v.type() == </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">typeid</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">(std::string))</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">    </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">std::cout &lt;&lt; get&lt;std::string&gt;(v) &lt;&lt; std::endl;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp comments\">// Else do nothing</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">main()</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::variant&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">, std::string&gt; v;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">v = </code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"Hello world\"</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">var_print(v);</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number18 index17 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">return</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">0;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number19 index18 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n使用RTTI技术可以避免类型访问错误而程序异常的情况，但是这样做有点不优雅，每增加一个类型，都需要修改if-else结构，并且使用RTTI会对程序性能有一定影响。\r\n\r\n<strong>使用访问者模式</strong>\r\n<div class=\"jb51code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_867840\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter cpp\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\"><a class=\"toolbar_item command_help help\" href=\"http://www.jb51.net/article/95814.htm#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">?</a></div>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\">10</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\">11</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\">12</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\">13</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\">14</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\">15</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\">16</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\">17</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number18 index17 alt1\">18</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number19 index18 alt2\">19</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">class</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">var_visitor : </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">public</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::static_visitor&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">void</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">public</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">:</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">void</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">operator()(</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">&amp; i) </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">const</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">    </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">std::cout &lt;&lt; i &lt;&lt; std::endl;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">void</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">operator()(std::string&amp; str) </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">const</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">    </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">std::cout &lt;&lt; str &lt;&lt; std::endl;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">};</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">main()</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::variant&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">, std::string&gt; v;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">v = </code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"Hello world\"</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::apply_visitor(var_visitor(), v);</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number18 index17 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">return</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">0;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number19 index18 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n使用该模式，需要定义一个类并继承于<code>boost::static_visitor</code>，在类里面需要重载()操作符，通过<code>boost::apply_visitor</code>来访问原始类型的值，这样做还是有些繁琐，每增加一个类型，都需要在var_visitor里面增加一个函数，但比使用RTTI里面的修改if-else结构好得多，因为使用访问者模式至少是遵循开放-封闭原则的，即对写开放，对修改封闭。\r\n\r\n<strong>使用模板函数</strong>\r\n<div class=\"jb51code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_427813\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter cpp\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\"><a class=\"toolbar_item command_help help\" href=\"http://www.jb51.net/article/95814.htm#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">?</a></div>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\">10</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\">11</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\">12</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\">13</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\">14</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\">15</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\">16</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">class</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">var_visitor : </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">public</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::static_visitor&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">void</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">public</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">:</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">template</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">typename</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">T&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">void</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">operator()(T&amp; i) </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">const</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">    </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">std::cout &lt;&lt; i &lt;&lt; std::endl;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">};</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">main()</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::variant&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">, std::string&gt; v;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">v = </code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"Hello world\"</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::apply_visitor(var_visitor(), v);</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">return</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">0;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n将<code>operator()</code>改成了模板函数的好处就是不用关心variant支持多少类型。','boost::any boost::variant boost::apply_visitor学习','','publish','open','open','','boostany-boostvariant-boostapply_visitor%e5%ad%a6%e4%b9%a0','','','2018-10-30 08:26:37','2018-10-30 08:26:37','',0,'http://45.77.202.181/?p=190',0,'post','',0),(191,1,'2018-10-30 08:25:05','2018-10-30 08:25:05','首先这些个类或函数的作用是用来替换早起union，因为早些时候的union是非类型安全的\r\n\r\nboost::any 和 boost::variant的区别\r\nboost::any一个类，包含特定的访问函数，但类型不限定\r\nboost::variant是一个模板类，模板形参规定了特定的几个类型，可以boost::get访问\r\nboost::apply_visitor则是用来访问boost::variant，由于boost::variant可能是多种类型，想让其调用对应的重载函数，就要使用boost::apply_visitor实际使用的使用lamda配合auto很方便，如\r\n\r\n<code class=\"EnlighterJSRAW\" data-enlighter-language=\"cpp\">auto successfulCallback = [&amp;](const messages::f1ap::CuConfigurationUpdateOutcome&amp; msg) {</code>\r\n<code class=\"EnlighterJSRAW\" data-enlighter-language=\"cpp\"> boost::apply_visitor([this](const auto&amp; msg) { this-&gt;onMessage(msg); }, msg);</code>\r\n<code class=\"EnlighterJSRAW\" data-enlighter-language=\"cpp\"> };</code>\r\n\r\nc++17增加的相应的支持\r\n如std::any std::variant std::visit\r\n\r\n<strong>以下文章转自：<a href=\"http://www.jb51.net/article/95814.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">http://www.jb51.net/article/95814.htm</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Boost.Variant</strong>\r\n\r\nVariant库包含一个不同于union的泛型类，用于在存储和操作来自于不同类型的对象。这个库的一个特点是支持类型安全的访问，减少了不同数据类型的类型转换代码的共同问题。\r\n\r\n<strong>Variant 库如何改进你的程序？</strong>\r\n\r\n•对用户指定的多种类型的进行类型安全的存储和取回\r\n\r\n•在标准库容器中存储不同类型的方法\r\n\r\n•变量访问的编译期检查\r\n\r\n•高效的、基于栈的变量存储\r\n\r\nVariant 库关注的是对一组限定类型的类型安全存储及取回，即非无类的联合。<code>Boost.Variant </code>库与<code> Boost.Any </code>有许多共同之外，但在功能上也有不同的考虑。在每天的编程中通常都会需要用到非无类的联合(不同的类型)。保持类型安全的一个典型方法是使用抽象基类，但这不总是可以做到的；即使可以做得，堆分配和虚拟函数的代价也可能太高。你也可以尝试用不安全的无类类型，如 void* (它会导致不幸)，或者是类型安全得无限制的可变类型，如 <code>Boost.Any</code>. 这里我们将看到 <code>Boost.Variant</code>，它支持限定的可变类型，即元素来自于一组支持的类型。\r\n\r\n下面将浅谈variant的几种访问方法，一起来学习学习吧。\r\n\r\n<strong>使用boost::get</strong>\r\n<div class=\"jb51code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_899793\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter cpp\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\"><a class=\"toolbar_item command_help help\" href=\"http://www.jb51.net/article/95814.htm#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">?</a></div>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::variant&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">, std::string&gt; v;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">v = </code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"Hello world\"</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">std::cout &lt;&lt; boost::get&lt;std::string&gt;(v) &lt;&lt; std::endl;</code></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n使用<code>boost::get</code>来访问，需要给出原始类型，并且这样做不安全，若类型错误，程序将会抛出异常。\r\n\r\n<strong>使用RTTI</strong>\r\n<div class=\"jb51code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_766693\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter cpp\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\"><a class=\"toolbar_item command_help help\" href=\"http://www.jb51.net/article/95814.htm#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">?</a></div>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\">10</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\">11</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\">12</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\">13</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\">14</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\">15</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\">16</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\">17</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number18 index17 alt1\">18</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number19 index18 alt2\">19</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">void</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">var_print(boost::variant&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">, std::string&gt;&amp; v)</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">if</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">(v.type() == </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">typeid</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">(</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">))</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">    </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">std::cout &lt;&lt; get&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">&gt;(v) &lt;&lt; std::endl;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">else</code> <code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">if</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">(v.type() == </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">typeid</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">(std::string))</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">    </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">std::cout &lt;&lt; get&lt;std::string&gt;(v) &lt;&lt; std::endl;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp comments\">// Else do nothing</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">main()</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::variant&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">, std::string&gt; v;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">v = </code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"Hello world\"</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">var_print(v);</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number18 index17 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">return</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">0;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number19 index18 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n使用RTTI技术可以避免类型访问错误而程序异常的情况，但是这样做有点不优雅，每增加一个类型，都需要修改if-else结构，并且使用RTTI会对程序性能有一定影响。\r\n\r\n<strong>使用访问者模式</strong>\r\n<div class=\"jb51code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_867840\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter cpp\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\"><a class=\"toolbar_item command_help help\" href=\"http://www.jb51.net/article/95814.htm#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">?</a></div>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\">10</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\">11</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\">12</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\">13</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\">14</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\">15</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\">16</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\">17</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number18 index17 alt1\">18</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number19 index18 alt2\">19</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">class</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">var_visitor : </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">public</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::static_visitor&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">void</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">public</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">:</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">void</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">operator()(</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">&amp; i) </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">const</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">    </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">std::cout &lt;&lt; i &lt;&lt; std::endl;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">void</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">operator()(std::string&amp; str) </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">const</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">    </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">std::cout &lt;&lt; str &lt;&lt; std::endl;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">};</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">main()</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::variant&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">, std::string&gt; v;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">v = </code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"Hello world\"</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number17 index16 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::apply_visitor(var_visitor(), v);</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number18 index17 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">return</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">0;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number19 index18 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n使用该模式，需要定义一个类并继承于<code>boost::static_visitor</code>，在类里面需要重载()操作符，通过<code>boost::apply_visitor</code>来访问原始类型的值，这样做还是有些繁琐，每增加一个类型，都需要在var_visitor里面增加一个函数，但比使用RTTI里面的修改if-else结构好得多，因为使用访问者模式至少是遵循开放-封闭原则的，即对写开放，对修改封闭。\r\n\r\n<strong>使用模板函数</strong>\r\n<div class=\"jb51code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"highlighter_427813\" class=\"syntaxhighlighter cpp\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\"><a class=\"toolbar_item command_help help\" href=\"http://www.jb51.net/article/95814.htm#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">?</a></div>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"gutter\">\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\">1</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\">2</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\">3</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\">4</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\">5</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\">6</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\">7</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\">8</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\">9</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\">10</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\">11</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\">12</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\">13</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\">14</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number15 index14 alt2\">15</div>\r\n<div class=\"line number16 index15 alt1\">16</div></td>\r\n<td class=\"code\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">class</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">var_visitor : </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">public</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::static_visitor&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">void</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">public</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">:</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">template</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">typename</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">T&gt;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">void</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">operator()(T&amp; i) </code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">const</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">    </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">std::cout &lt;&lt; i &lt;&lt; std::endl;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number8 index7 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number9 index8 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">};</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number10 index9 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code> <code class=\"cpp plain\">main()</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number11 index10 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number12 index11 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::variant&lt;</code><code class=\"cpp color1 bold\">int</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">, std::string&gt; v;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number13 index12 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">v = </code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"Hello world\"</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">;</code></div>\r\n<div class=\"line number14 index13 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">  </code><code class=\"cpp plain\">boost::apply_visitor(var_visitor(), v);</code></div>\r\n<div 