trate (please use -b:v)\", \"bitrate\" },\r\n\r\n例如 -b:a 96k -b:v 500k\r\n\r\n6、视频常用\r\n{ \"r\", OPT_VIDEO | HAS_ARG | OPT_STRING | OPT_SPEC |\r\nOPT_INPUT | OPT_OUTPUT, { .off = OFFSET(frame_rates) },\r\n\"set frame rate (Hz value, fraction or abbreviation)\", \"rate\" },\r\n{ \"s\", OPT_VIDEO | HAS_ARG | OPT_SUBTITLE | OPT_STRING | OPT_SPEC |\r\nOPT_INPUT | OPT_OUTPUT, { .off = OFFSET(frame_sizes) },\r\n\"set frame size (WxH or abbreviation)\", \"size\" },\r\n例如 -r 25 -s 640*480\r\n\r\n这些选项作用于哪个文件，就看选项后面的是哪个文件结尾的\r\n<h1>从代码来分析ffmpeg的使用</h1>\r\n1、参数上下文\r\ntypedef struct OptionParseContext {\r\nOptionGroup global_opts;\r\n\r\nOptionGroupList *groups;\r\nint nb_groups;\r\n\r\n/* parsing state */\r\nOptionGroup cur_group;\r\n} OptionParseContext;\r\nnb_groups等于2，说明有两个OptionGroupList，一个是输入组，一个输出组\r\n说明ffmpeg支持多个输入文件和多个输出文件\r\n\r\n2、一个输入组或输出组\r\ntypedef struct OptionGroupList {\r\nconst OptionGroupDef *group_def;\r\n\r\nOptionGroup *groups;\r\nint nb_groups;\r\n} OptionGroupList;\r\n一个输入组或输出组可以包含nb_groups文件\r\n\r\n3、文件选项\r\ntypedef struct OptionGroup {\r\nconst OptionGroupDef *group_def;\r\nconst char *arg;\r\n\r\nOption *opts;\r\nint nb_opts;\r\n\r\nAVDictionary *codec_opts;\r\nAVDictionary *format_opts;\r\nAVDictionary *resample_opts;\r\nAVDictionary *sws_dict;\r\nAVDictionary *swr_opts;\r\n} OptionGroup;\r\n一个文件选项可以包含nb_opts个选项\r\n\r\n4、输入组或输出组\r\nstatic const OptionGroupDef groups[] = {\r\n[GROUP_OUTFILE] = { \"output url\", NULL, OPT_OUTPUT },\r\n[GROUP_INFILE] = { \"input url\", \"i\", OPT_INPUT },\r\n};\r\n输入文件用-i分隔，输出文件不需要','ffmpeg命令行','','inherit','closed','closed','','234-revision-v1','','','2019-01-18 05:48:34','2019-01-18 05:48:34','',234,'http://45.77.202.181/?p=244',0,'revision','',0),(246,1,'2019-02-23 02:58:03','2019-02-23 02:58:03','1、对于有特化版本，且能匹配特化版本，是优先匹配特化版本的\r\n\r\n1.1\r\n<pre class=\"EnlighterJSRAW\" data-enlighter-language=\"null\">template &lt;class T1 = int&gt;\r\nvoid fun()\r\n{\r\n    cout&lt;&lt;\"000\"&lt;&lt;endl;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\ntemplate &